Messy Meta Ads exports are the bane of every SMM's existence. Generic AI tools fail because they don't understand marketing context. Our AI doesn't just read the data; it understands it. The 'One-Click Clean' feature recognizes your exports, cleans the formatting, and prepares your ROI analysis instantly. No more manual copy-paste errors. Book a 10-minute demo to see how Social Logic can transform your reporting workflow.

